<paragraph id="8B8736DCB9583C05FF6B5260B8653E37" blockId="2.[151,1118,746,830]" box="[151,531,808,830]" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">Station AB 159 (MNHN S2 HAL 55)</paragraph>
